    <item>
      <title>特朗普下令加快美国各地项目审批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-plan-to-speed-permitting-of-projects-across-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令加快联邦许可的发放，以此吸引美国投资并缩短关键能源基础设施的建设时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-plan-to-speed-permitting-of-projects-across-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 20:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普迷惑市场 关税推迟 股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/tesla-slides-space-stocks-soar-after-trump-s-barrage-of-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普第二任期开始一个交易日后，很明显股市有了新的驱动力，至少目前如此。周二股价上涨，涨幅主要源于总统没有做的一件事：对主要贸易伙伴实施全面关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/tesla-slides-space-stocks-soar-after-trump-s-barrage-of-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普的关税措施旨在制造混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正试图在其贸易伙伴中制造不确定性，以使他们失去平衡并削弱他们的谈判地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普继续威胁征收关税，大宗商品价格回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对墨西哥和加拿大发出关税威胁，再次引发贸易战担忧，石油和工业金属价格下跌，而黄金价格则因投资者寻求避险资产而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂缓征收关税，股市获人工智能提振：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普总统对全球贸易的言论好于预期，人们越来越多地猜测他的政策将进一步提振美国企业，股市随之上涨。债券继续回吐近期令市场动荡的收益率飙升。美元波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 22:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
